core":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T16:19:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WGkQMToCnhw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWGkQMToCnhw&d=LEs%2BwAtQgaw8rqlH5r8IfL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a84fd011\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WGkQMToCnhw</a><br />\n香港對馬來西亞精華"},{"pid":"77c2e76ae93f2b07756f9f8789d0c5dec7f0d86f","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T19:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4502aaa859f1a9f70cf86b13b32eb492669dfa","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:52:05.000Z","msg":"香港隊克服馬來西亞潮濕天氣的影響，上週六在主隊身上攻入10次達陣並以67-8取得大捷，順利跨過2019年日本世界盃晉級之路的第一道關卡。   <br />\n<br />\n港隊今仗完全掌控戰局，賽事戰至40分鐘天公開始不造美，但港隊並未太受濕滑環境影響，上半場已輕鬆領先27-5，直至以67-8取得今季亞洲欖球錦標賽的首勝。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞陣中有7名太平洋島國的歸化兵，戰鬥力因而提升不少並取得不俗的開局，而港隊的罰球劊子手羅斯尼初段腳風不順，射失幾個罰球。<br />\n<br />\n港隊持續在鬥牛和界外球方面取得壓倒性優勢，於30分鐘造就林保利梅開二度，香港領先至13-0。<br />\n<br />\n下半場甫開賽不久，馬來西亞的解圍誤落羅斯尼手中，他將大禮送予姚錦成完成達陣。主隊犯下這大意失誤後士氣急速下滑，因此讓姚錦成再有機可乘並梅開二度，一下子將分數擴大至39-5。<br />\n<br />\n主隊在完場前從48米外射入超長程罰球，總算為8-67的敗局取回些場安慰。"},{"pid":"3abe89f6168b7011bb256365b0c2c70959b47463","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T07:23:16.000Z","msg":"原來係南韓時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港應該係15:30先岩"},{"pid":"c74990a2cee8746506924f0861b3036c9a4dc0f7","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T09:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f2e782ed3569b01da265d2e0aebb90100b455f","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4192bb6ad8436b49d3cfe4ca206c13219d018fcc","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/b556b2375666dd561d70fb0a57a41ac5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fb556b2375666dd561d70fb0a57a41ac5.jpg&h=041c4403&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24432a8bee235931abda3fa45000765ae6b7569d","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T03:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023ec89a32852f1025ad974595ce8c106e1e7975","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"ARC Division III East<br />\nHalftime<br />\nGuam 31-0 China<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6086421880f3b13214952434c8c1fb450766a4ae","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"關島 52-12 中國"},{"pid":"09afed7715750eff7fbef2cfe1340f00587ef469","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T02:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef0caa5f39bd22ec741aaca80951c8d5a1a554b","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港隊正選名單<br />\n<br />\nForwards: 1. Daniel Barlow, 2. Ben Roberts, 3. Dylan Rogers, 4. James Cunningham (captain), 5. Kyle Sullivan, 6. Nicholas Hewson, 7. Toby Fenn, 8. Thomas Lamboley<br />\n<br />\nBacks: 9. Liam Slatem, 10. Matthew Rosslee, 11. Max Denmark, 13. Tyler Spitz, 12. Max Woodward, 14. Salom Yiu Kam Shing, 15. Jack Neville<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"249a8c2fd8bf5d4034a0bc7a3e4536d4c53e36b7","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"港隊在近五次南韓皆獲全勝，雖然對賽往績佔優，不過隊長根寧咸(Jamie Cunningham)認為作客到訪韓國不能掉以輕心。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「對手身型強壯，在前線有一定優勢，我們需要打出上週的水準，並加快比賽節奏令對方難以防範。」<br />\n<br />\n「南韓打法非常硬朗，但只要我們做到賽前部署，並有理想的發揮，相信己方可取勝獨佔榜首之位。」<br />\n<br />\n根寧咸續道：「南韓天氣比較乾燥，相比馬來西亞的潮濕天氣較為理想，我期望球隊能夠保持控球權，並嘗試做更多推進，相信這樣便可以取得二連勝。」"},{"pid":"9eb8cf1852b026b64209f13f6d4b1bd27d051c85","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff626634a72a96d2241f250493f7237595d3e43","tid":657660,"uid":25251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"其實入到世界盃機會大唔大？<br />\n最大阻力係canada?<br />\n仲有咩潛在對手"},{"pid":"8208c17387d3c06841aabae25c7b0c7ee7188da9","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8f00736ea96508c8e8ede95219364732cf8492","tid":657660,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}